<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>AI Call Center Platform — Case Study</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav">
  <div class="nav__logo">Irina Shytsik</div>
  <nav>
    <a href="index.html">Back</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="case-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>AI-powered Call Center Platform</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Reducing agent workload and improving efficiency through AI-assisted workflows
    </p>

    <div class="case-metrics">
      <div><strong>+35%</strong><span>Agent efficiency</span></div>
      <div><strong>-40%</strong><span>Handling time</span></div>
      <div><strong>+22%</strong><span>Resolution rate</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Context</h2>
    <p>
      A web-based platform designed for customer support teams to manage high volumes of incoming calls.
      The system integrates AI to assist agents with real-time recommendations, automation, and insights.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Platform: Web (desktop-first)</li>
      <li>Role: Product Designer (end-to-end)</li>
      <li>Scope: Dashboard, call interface, AI assistant</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section dark">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Problem</h2>
    <p>
      Agents were overwhelmed by complex workflows, switching between multiple tools,
      and manually handling repetitive tasks during calls.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>High cognitive load</li>
      <li>Slow response time</li>
      <li>Inconsistent customer experience</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Insight</h2>
    <p>
      Agents don’t need more tools — they need contextual assistance during live interactions.
    </p>

    <p>
      The key opportunity was to embed AI directly into the workflow,
      reducing decision-making time and guiding agents in real time.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section dark">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Solution</h2>

    <div class="solution-grid">

      <div class="solution">
        <h3>AI Assistant Panel</h3>
        <p>
          Real-time suggestions based on conversation context,
          including recommended responses and actions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="solution">
        <h3>Unified Interface</h3>
        <p>
          Combined call controls, customer data, and actions in one screen
          to eliminate context switching.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="solution">
        <h3>Automated Workflows</h3>
        <p>
          Reduced manual tasks with auto-fill, tagging, and call summaries.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Impact</h2>

    <ul class="impact">
      <li><strong>+35%</strong> agent efficiency</li>
      <li><strong>-40%</strong> average handling time</li>
      <li><strong>+22%</strong> issue resolution rate</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      The redesign significantly improved agent performance and reduced operational costs.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section dark">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Key Decisions</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Embedded AI into workflow instead of separate tools</li>
      <li>Prioritised clarity over feature density</li>
      <li>Designed for speed and real-time interaction</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="case-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Next Steps</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Predictive recommendations based on history</li>
      <li>Voice interaction for hands-free control</li>
      <li>Personalised agent dashboards</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
